data.description: Welcome to a spacious and versatile haven of comfort, boasting 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and a generous 5600 square feet of well-designed living space. This distinguished residence offers an extraordinary floor plan tailored for modern living, featuring the convenience of a 2-car garage. Nestled in a sought-after location, this home welcomes you with a blend of functionality and elegance. The thoughtful design includes 2 full baths on the main level, providing a unique opportunity for generational living. Whether you envision an In-law or Owner's suite on the main floor, this layout caters to various needs, ensuring flexibility for your lifestyle. The large kitchen with ample counter space, is a culinary enthusiast's dream. The adjacent dining and living areas flow together, creating an ideal space for intimate family gatherings and grand entertainment. Upstairs, discover the 2nd master suite and a collection of generously sized bedrooms, each bathed in natural light and offering a retreat-like atmosphere. The master suite, with its luxurious ensuite bathroom, provides a private sanctuary for relaxation.  The two-car garage ensures convenience and practicality, while the potential for generational living adds a layer of versatility to the property. Embrace the opportunity to create a separate living space for extended family or utilize it as a source of additional income, such as a corporate rental or Airbnb. Step outside to a rocking chair front porch overlooking a spacious front lawn with an eastward-facing view of Atlanta's skyline. Property zoning (R5) allows for a range of possibilities, making it an investment opportunity or a welcoming home for multi-generational living. Located in a desirable community with easy access to amenities, schools, and entertainment, this residence presents a unique blend of style and functionality. Don't miss the chance to make this versatile property your place where comfort, convenience, and endless possibilities converge. Welcome home to a lifestyle of unparalleled adaptability and luxury.
